query:
INSERT INTO contracts (producerId, actorId, projectTitle, paymentTerms, paymentAmount, startDate, endDate, deliverables, status, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM users WHERE userRole = 'producer' LIMIT 1) as producerId,
  id as actorId,
  CASE 
    WHEN name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN 'Feature Film - The Last Stand'
    WHEN name = 'Michael Chen' THEN 'TV Series - Crime Drama'
    WHEN name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN 'Independent Film - Coming of Age'
    WHEN name = 'David Kim' THEN 'Voice Over - Animation'
    WHEN name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN 'Theater Production - Shakespeare'
  END as projectTitle,
  'Payment upon completion' as paymentTerms,
  CASE 
    WHEN name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN '5000.00'
    WHEN name = 'Michael Chen' THEN '8000.00'
    WHEN name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN '3000.00'
    WHEN name = 'David Kim' THEN '1500.00'
    WHEN name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN '4000.00'
  END as paymentAmount,
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 90 DAY) as startDate,
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 30 DAY) as endDate,
  'Professional performance and deliverables' as deliverables,
  'completed' as status,
  NOW() as createdAt,
  NOW() as updatedAt
FROM users 
WHERE userRole = 'actor' AND openId LIKE 'sample_actor_%'
